read a six digit number from user 
store it in variable x
check if x is greater than 0
it will enter the if loop
Take the remainder of the number by modulo of 10 it will give last digit
take last digit store in the variable
divide the x with 10 the last digit is lost
again run the loop using goto 
use the same procedure and get the remainder
now multipy the previvous remainder with 10 and add the second remainder to it
repeat till the x is gretaer then 0
print the value at the end reverse value is printed 
